             sworn.</p>
               <p>I was standing at <placeName id="t17760522-44-crimeloc198">Bear-key</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17760522-44-crimeloc198" type="placeName" value="Bear-key"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17760522-44-crimeloc198" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17760522-44-off195 t17760522-44-crimeloc198"></join> about five o'clock in the evening; I saw the prisoner take the parcel and put it in his apron, and go up the gate-way, I followed him; there was a cart stood in the gate-way that he could not get by; he dropped the parcel; Mansfield, who was with me, took it up, and we secured him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17760522-44-person557">
                  John
                   Mansfield
